CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1773990267
OL,3,CHospital apologises after 21 patients
OL,4,Ctreated with non-sterile instruments
OL,6,FAneurin Bevan University Health Board,
OL,7,Fwhich governs the hospital, said all
OL,8,Faffected patients had been contacted.
OL,10,FIn the error, the instruments had
OL,11,Fcompleted their initial cleaning and
OL,12,Fdisinfection stages but did not go
OL,13,Fthrough final sterilisation before
OL,14,Fbeing reused.
OL,16,FThe patients affected will now undergo
OL,17,F"precautionary testing" to see if they
OL,18,Fhave contracted any possible viruses
OL,19,Fas a result of the incident.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
