OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1773990267
OL,3,CHospital apologises after 21 patients
OL,4,Ctreated with non-sterile instruments
OL,6,FA spokesman for Aneurin Bevan
OL,7,FUniversity Health Board said:
OL,8,F"Following an issue affecting the
OL,9,Fsterilisation of a very small number
OL,10,Fof medical instruments at the Royal
OL,11,FGwent Hospital, we are taking
OL,12,Fprecautionary steps to support the 21
OL,13,Fpatients affected. Although the
OL,14,Finstruments completed the initial
OL,15,Fcleaning and disinfection stages, they
OL,16,Fdid not go through the final
OL,17,Fsterilisation phase.
OL,26,@pD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
