PN,46904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1773990267
OL,3,CHospital apologises after 21 patients
OL,4,Ctreated with non-sterile instruments
OL,6,F"We have already contacted the
OL,7,Fpatients affected and want to offer
OL,8,Four sincere and heartfelt apologies
OL,9,Ffor the worry this situation may
OL,10,Fcause. While the clinical risk of
OL,11,FBloodBorne Virus exposure is
OL,12,Fextremely low, we have arranged
OL,13,Fprecautionary testing and support to
OL,14,Fgive full reassurance.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/6
