PN,46905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1773990267
OL,3,CHospital apologises after 21 patients
OL,4,Ctreated with non-sterile instruments
OL,6,F"We fully recognise the concern and
OL,7,Fdistress this may cause, and we are
OL,8,Ftruly sorry. The wellbeing of our
OL,9,Fpatients is our highest priority, and
OL,10,Fwe are taking all necessary actions to
OL,11,Funderstand how this happened and to
OL,12,Fprevent it from occurring again.
OL,14,F"We also understand that others may
OL,15,Ffeel concerned on hearing about this.
OL,16,FWe want to reassure all patients that
OL,17,Fthis was a very limited incident,
OL,18,Fthose affected have been contacted
OL,19,Fdirectly, and there is no wider cause
OL,20,Ffor concern."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU|D@MO]
